version_description:
1) More totems generate;

2) Gem totem destruction inflicts more damage to the Kings;

3) Goblin Shaman's ability to increase the blocks' rigidity is no more active after the King's defeat; mine layers' depth rebalanced;

4) Kobold king: objects number rebalanced in the first digging games:
- fewer stones,
- more energy,
- more crates (and fewer snakes inside them);

5) Fixed the issue with Mortars and TNT killing hero at the start of the digging game.

Dear treasure-seekers, an update is already available, and the subterranean adventures must go on! Hot news:
— check out the new features of the Arsenal – now you can obtain the Permanent Aim and use it throughout the event;
— the Heart Hunter event is back again, renewed, and even more exciting – the further you dig, the more hearts you collect;
— the Leaderboards and Store were significantly improved;
— added: ads board – receive extra rewards for watching ads.
